  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Mutt</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Mutt</application> package contains a Mail User
      Agent. This is useful for reading, writing, replying to, saving, and
      deleting your email.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

